name: test_CMS_11_6_0_Mark_Multiple_Notifications_As_Read
description:
Test Case 205: Verify that marking multiple notifications as read works correctly.

Test Steps:
1. Launch the browser
2. Login as admin user
3. Navigate to Notifications page
4. Mark multiple notifications as read (up to 3)
5. Verify each notification is marked as read
descriptionHtml:
